translation[17]{c,v,t}:
  23,1,Chisimu pamasile paapundile ŵakulupilila
  23,2,Aŵala ŵaakuŵa ŵakuteteŵala pa Swala syao
  23,3,Ni aŵala ŵaakuŵa nkuitundumalila yangali mate
  23,4,Ni aŵala ŵaakuŵa nkutenda yakutola Zaka
  23,5,Ni aŵala ŵaakuŵa nkuugosa utukani wao
  23,6,"Ikaŵeje (akuukamulichisya masengo) pa achiŵammakwao kapena yagapatile makono gao gakun’dyo (mateka), basi chisimu ŵanganyao nganaŵa ŵagambidwa"
  23,7,"Sano ŵatasache yakuipunda yele, basi ŵanyao ni ŵakusumba mpika"
  23,8,Ni aŵala ŵaakuŵa nkusunga ichindu yaasunjisyidwe kwisa soni ilanga yao
  23,9,Ni aŵala ŵaakuŵa nkusigosa Swala syao (pakusiswali chenene mundaŵi syakwe)
  23,10,Ŵanganyao ni akutawala
  23,11,"Aŵala ŵatakajitawale Mbepo ja Firdausi, ŵanyao mwalakwemo takaŵe ŵandamo"
  23,12,Soni chisimu Uwwe twan’gumbile mundu (Adam) kuumila mwilongo lyesaguche
  23,13,"Kaneko twantesile (mundu jwalijose kuŵa jwagumbidwa ni) lindondwa (lya ulume ni ukongwe, lyalikuŵichidwaga) pa malo pakutamilichika ni kusunjika chenene (mu chiŵelechelo)"
  23,14,"Kaneka ni tukasaligalausyaga lindondwalila kuŵa chipande chamyasi, ni tukasachigalausyaga chipande chamyasichila kuŵa chipande channou, ni tukasachigalausyaga chipande channouchila kuŵa maupa, ni tukasagawechaga maupagala minou, kaneko ni tukasantendaga kuŵa chiumbe chine (chaumi pakumpepelela nsimu). Basi atukwiche (pa uchimbichimbi ni upile) Allah, jwali Jwambone nnope mwa akugumba"
  23,15,Soni chisimu ŵanganyammwe panyuma payalakweyo tim’bwe
  23,16,Soni chisimu ŵanganyammwe lisiku lya Kiyama tinchiukulidwa m’malembe
  23,17,"Soni chisimu Uwwe twagumbile pachanya penu matala nsano nagaŵili (mawunde), ni nganituŵa Uwwe ŵanti ningaimanya iwumbe"